content.rendered:
Electrical and Diagnostic Services

New vehicles are especially dependent on their computer systems, which is why advanced computer and internal diagnostics are essential for determining the cause of a problem

Using the latest diagnostic and scanning tools it is only a matter of time until our team of technicians will find the issue with any electrical problem as well as a solution to it.

If you can’t see the service you’re looking for, get in touch and our experts can advise you on what we can offer.

 

What can we help with?

  • Intake systems
  • Car security
  • ECU
  • Diesel diagnostic and EFI
  • Door locks & Power windows
  • Engine carbon clean
  • Engine lights
  • Fuel injection system
  • SRS and Airbags
  • Starter motors, Batteries, Alternators
  • All other car electrics

ALL WORK GUARANTEED
